OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1784810902
OL,3,CFirefighters tackling blaze in
OL,4,CArmathwaite
OL,6,FFirefighters have been working through
OL,7,Fthe night to contain a fire in
OL,8,FArmathwaite, south of Carlisle.
OL,10,FCumbria Fire and Rescue Service said
OL,11,Feight fire engines have been in
OL,12,Fattendance since 7.34pm yesterday (22
OL,13,FJuly) and they were continuing to
OL,14,Fbattle to extinguish the fire this
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FPolice say it is believed to be at an
OL,18,Fempty building and there are no
OL,19,Freported casualties.
