OL,3,CFirefighters tackling blaze in
OL,4,CArmathwaite
OL,6,FNearby residents are advised to keep
OL,7,Fwindows and doors closed as there is
OL,8,Fsmoke in the air.
OL,10,FRoad closures are in place. Cumbria
OL,11,FPolice have asked people to avoid the
OL,12,Farea and not to attend the scene.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
